name: Ana Fidalgo
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
I’m an active person who enjoys the outdoors and to see the world around me. Whenever I get the chance to travel, I always take the opportunity to capture those moments with my camera.

I’ve always had a strong passion for all things Web, which led me to a degree in New Communication Technologies and the pursuit of a career in Web Development.

Recently I discovered the amazing world of Video Editing – an area I had the opportunity to explore during my early professional career. Although not one of my main focus at my work, I definitely developed a liking in this area.
In short, if you’re looking for someone who can create awesome videos, develop amazing websites or take some great professional pictures, then your search is over. Just head to my contact page and send me an email.
